<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Validar Código - Logic Beauty</title>
    <style>
        /* CSS exato do painel administrativo */
        :root {
            --sidebar-dark: #4A2E35;
            --accent-gold: #f4C2C2;
            --bg-light: #F1F1F1;
            --success-green: #B76E79;
        }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
        body { background-color: var(--bg-light); display: flex; height: 100vh; overflow: hidden; color: #4A2E35; }

        .sidebar { width: 80px; background-color: var(--sidebar-dark); display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; padding-top: 20px; }
        .sidebar-logo { width: 40px; height: 40px; border: 2px solid var(--accent-gold); border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 40px; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; color: var(--accent-gold); font-weight: bold; }
        .menu-icon { width: 100%; padding: 20px 0; text-align: center; color: rgba(241, 241, 241, 0.5); font-size: 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; }
        
        .main-content { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }
        .top-nav { background-color: white; padding: 0 40px; display: flex; gap: 30px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaec; height: 60px; align-items: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .tab-btn { background: none; border: none; padding: 18px 0; color: var(--sidebar-dark); font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; border-bottom: 3px solid var(--sidebar-dark); }

        .view-container { display: flex; gap: 30px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 30px; height: calc(100vh - 60px); overflow-y: auto; }
        
        .left-panel { width: 400px; background-color: #faf9fa; border: 1px solid #eaeaec; border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .left-panel h3 { margin-bottom: 25px; color: var(--sidebar-dark); font-size: 1.1rem; }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .form-group label { display: block; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--sidebar-dark); font-weight: 600; }
        .form-group input { width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px; outline: none; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--sidebar-dark); }
        .form-group input:focus { border-color: var(--accent-gold); }
        
        .btn-submit { background-color: var(--success-green); color: white; border: none; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 10px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .btn-submit:hover { background-color: #4A2E35; }
        
        .right-panel { flex: 1; background-color: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.02); overflow-y: auto; max-height: 100%; }
        .system-title { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--sidebar-dark); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-logo">LB</div>
        <a href="/login" class="menu-icon" title="Voltar ao Login">🔙</a>
    </aside>

    <main class="main-content">
        <header class="top-nav">
            <div class="tab-btn">Recuperação de Acesso</div>
        </header>

        <div class="view-container">
            <section class="left-panel">
                <h3>Validar Código</h3>
                <form action="/verificar-codigo" method="POST" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="codigoInput">Código de Verificação de 6 dígitos</label>
                        <input type="text" id="codigoInput" name="codigo" placeholder="Ex: 123456" pattern="[0-9]{6}" required maxlength="6" style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.2rem; letter-spacing: 8px; font-weight: bold;">
                    </div>
                    
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">✓ Verificar Código</button>
                    <a href="/login" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #888; text-decoration: none;">Cancelar e voltar</a>
                </form>
            </section>

            <section class="right-panel">
                <h1 class="system-title">LOGIC BEAUTY</h1>
                <p style="color: #888; margin-bottom: 40px;">Segurança da Conta</p>
                <div style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">
                    <p>Enviamos um código de segurança temporário para o e-mail: <strong style="color: var(--sidebar-dark);"><%= email %></strong></p><br>
                    <p>• <strong>Atenção:</strong> Este código expira em 15 minutos.</p>
                    <p>• <strong>Não recebeu?</strong> Verifique sua caixa de Spam ou Lixo Eletrônico.</p>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>




